plot: Caitlyn Jenner proudly announces her true self to the world, but still has a hard time with meeting some of her family for the first time; Caitlyn is inspired to learn more about transgender youth in crisis.

In the series premiere, Caitlyn Jenner proudly announces her true self to the world via Vanity Fair, but still struggles with meeting some of her family for the first time. Meanwhile, Caitlyn is also inspired to learn more about transgender youth in crisis.
